smartie-utils is a set or utilities for sureelectronics' LCD Smartie USB
screens (http://www.sureelectronics.net/goods.php?id=964) and other Matrix
Orbital-compatible devices.

Requires Tcl >= 8.4.

smartie-ctl  --- set display contrast and configura backlight
smartie-cat  --- output text to a display
smartie-tail --- tail stdin to a display

Author:         Alexander Galanin <al@galanin.nnov.ru>
Home page:      http://galanin.nnov.ru/~al/
Project home:   http://code.google.com/p/smartie-utils/

